{"root":{"data":{"id":"d3rc8jbk7r40","created":1724827266389,"text":"定语从句(一整句话充当adj)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rc8qk9jqw0","created":1724827282153,"text":"做题方式","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rc9bnbf5c0","created":1724827328050,"text":"1.主从分离\n2.找到句子里面的先行词\n3.判断句子缺不缺成分\n4.确定关系词","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcaj118m80","created":1724827422481,"text":"关系代词(定语从句缺成分)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcbdnihxs0","created":1724827489144,"text":"人:who(主)    whom(宾)    that(主/宾/表)\n物:which(主/宾)   that(主/宾/表)\n的:whose   先行词和定语从句的主语成所属关系\n省略:以上的关系代词在定语从句中充当宾语的时候可以省略","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcd4twms00","created":1724827626668,"text":"补充考点as的用法\n1.定语从句缺成分 （主/宾/表)\n2.先行词被such/the same所修饰的时候","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcakg9u200","created":1724827425579,"text":"关系副词(定语从句不缺成分)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcebzhrx40","created":1724827720607,"text":"When      先行词是时间\nWhere     先行词是地点\nWhy         先行词是原因","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3rceykkirc0","created":1724827769771,"text":"补充考点:当先行词是the way 的时候，定语从句的引导词可以用that/in which/省略","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcaq2eym00","created":1724827437802,"text":"介词+关系代词","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcfvwilk80","created":1724827842327,"text":"定语从句不缺成分,但是选项中没有关系副词或者选择关系副词不合适","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcgju4snc0","created":1724827894426,"text":"介词+which     先行词是物\n介词+whom     先行词是人","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3rch2egexs0","created":1724827934837,"text":"介词如何选择\n1.当先行词不是特定的先行词的时候，我们需要看定语从句里面谓语动词的搭配\n2.当先行词是特定的先行词的时候，我们需要根据特定的先行词来选择介词\n①方面/领域  respect/aspect/area/filed     in\n②价格/利率/速度    price/rate/speed        at\n③程度    degree/extend                   to\n④基础    basic/base/ground/foundation   on","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcav6n5gg0","created":1724827448942,"text":"定语从句的分类(有无逗号)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcjrfh4o80","created":1724828146046,"text":"非限制性定语从句","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rck2qp12g0","created":1724828170669,"text":"1.在非限制性定语从句中，不用that\n2.which可以指代前面的一整句话翻译成“这”","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcl2km0zs0","created":1724828248665,"text":"as引导的非限制性定语从句都是固定搭配\nas is known to all= as we all know 众所周知\nas is often the case 通常是这样\nas often happens  事实往往如此\nas is expected 不出所料\nas is mentioned/said/reported  正如所提及的/说的/报道的","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcaxzbryw0","created":1724827455030,"text":"that的用法","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcmd8jwi80","created":1724828350245,"text":"不用that的情况","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcmgoh5lk0","created":1724828357738,"text":"①空前有介词的情况下\n②非限制性定语从句中","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcmyjw5uo0","created":1724828396643,"text":"只用that的情况","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcn1kqo680","created":1724828403225,"text":"最:当先行词被最高级/序数词/the only/the very/the just/the last\n不:当先行词是不定代词或者先行词被不定代词所修饰的时候\n避:为了避免重复只用that\n人物:当先行词有人又有物的情况下","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d3rcb0fldzk0","created":1724827460367,"text":"特殊用法","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d3rcommio2o0","created":1724828527409,"text":"1.代词/数词 +of which/whom(代词/数词也可以放在后面)  往往先行词被数量词修饰\n2.定语从句的插入语问题    主+think/believe/suppose/guess/imagine (往往位于主 谓之间)\n3.定语从句的单复数问题\none of +可数名词的复数形式            复\nthe one of +可数名词的复数形式     单","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}